<h2>My 5 day fast</h2>
<p>About a month ago or so I added <em>Support my Muslim friends by taking part in Ramadan</em> to my bucket list - I’d wanted to do it last year to support colleagues and friends but couldn’t bring myself to even try.</p>
<p>This year I intended on fasting but still drinking for the 5 day working week, and actually managed to go without any fluids as well as food during the daylight hours.</p>
<p>Most days this involved eating at approximately 9:40pm when the sun goes down and eating ’til around 10pm, drinking a lot of iced water then sleeping. I’d wake up during the night and down a couple more pints of water but then that was it until 9:40 the following evening.</p>

